if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n銀行工 14K</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9be87bbd5a2b518ef27ca4388b9c67d5e90c98e","tid":102608,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:11:36.000Z","msg":"09年 third hon 畢業 (HR, 成績真係剛剛好夠畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n同年入左大地產公司做個文員仔 $8000 兩個月未夠比人兜左 (應該係比人拎左黎做替死鬼)<br />\n之後糧左幾個月地到12月政府請外判大會堂看更<br />\n做左2個月<br />\n到10年2月有間壽險公司請左做temp<br />\n做左1年幾不斷renew contract 到第三次遞信 (有offer)<br />\n咁岩又有個同事走, 所以轉左我做perm, 一路又做左年幾<br />\n到12年中比人點名轉走左上母公司 (呢個真係因為同上司唔夾, 佢地又咁夾有呢個需要, 做個順手丟走我)<br />\n母公司做左大半年冇發展 (純做payroll)<br />\n13年中走左去一間MNC度做<br />\n轉左去工作真係非常豐富<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但經過公司多次restructure, M&amp;A, 結果我又做到幾乎淨係做payroll<br />\n多次同上司反映同屌鬼 (由14年中開始持續到走, 因為入黎做既原意唔係咁)<br />\n咁最後當然係不歡而散 (變左做problem staff)<br />\n其實上司係好人, 又有料跟到佢學到好多野, 但再對上個仆街太西<br />\n我上司都係yes man, 真係冇計, 幫佢頂左兩年幾屎頂到嘔<br />\n(幾乎成個APAC既payroll 都係關我事)<br />\n上年16年尾有offer<br />\n頭也不回走左<br />\n而家係一間世界都幾有名既資產管理公司度做<br />\n做左三個月暫時仍然同份JD係一致 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(即係冇話呢D關關地你事又比埋你做之類)<br />\n<br />\n做左6-7年野(都係HR)<br />\n人工30k上下<br />\n而家呢份工做既野暫時都係唔太有挑戰 (好舒適下)<br />\n有冇前途見仁見智<br />\n行行出狀員呢句都係真既<br />\n<br />\n覺得自己比上不足比下有餘<br />\n工作關係見太多勁人<br />\n同一界既係壽險公司既buddy都經理級以上<br />\n講緊係搵6-70k<br />\n呢D真係睇際遇同個人努力<br />\n遇到一個睇你既老闆真係好可貴<br />\n唔洗多睇你一兩年已經上左火箭咁<br />\n亦見過不少際遇平平什至差既<br />\n<br />\n成績重唔重要真係好睇行業同工種<br />\n除非你係講緊好專業果類:如精算 投資 等等<br />\n但大部分都唔會好著重...有張大學畢業證書其實都唔好點理你咩成績"},{"pid":"2670791cf28eb97ccbb9d93cb27ea47aa05d8fd2","tid":102608,"uid":41944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:29:05.000Z","msg":"third hon<br />\n讀緊U 個陣掛住揾錢，結果defer 足兩年先畢到業<br />\n大學未畢業已經有車有首期買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87f0425fd044435c53c7e5e50886c5ec80885fe","tid":102608,"uid":22283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>third hon<br />\n讀緊U 個陣掛住揾錢，結果defer 足兩年先畢到業<br />\n大學未畢業已經有車有首期買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係咁<br />\n用左讀U三年時間 搵錢<br />\n依加上左車買左樓<br />\n<br />\n就打番工算數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 無defer 三年時間準時畢業"},{"pid":"e3e72a0d1fa583eadd061b8b450a4b989a3f9add","tid":102608,"uid":43150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T09:18:38.000Z","msg":"報AO直接DQ就係因為個hon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過真係其他人唔多理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79e983b73efa635e3f1767e914298ef00043463","tid":102608,"uid":47883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"乜bank mt都過唔到screening<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be03d03c350e83fd830bedd5883390557bcf8d8","tid":102608,"uid":15776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"就快grad，頭痛緊點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d733603c98f4cb082e783b62f39e9ad873b2c1","tid":102608,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T17:49:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜bank mt都過唔到screening<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/c